                      </ul>
                      <p>The course usually runs over a <strong>weekend (Saturday and Sunday)</strong> from 9:30 AM to around 16:30 PM daily. It is <strong>day-sailing only</strong>, with no overnight stays unless part of a longer package.</p>
                      <p>Want to keep progressing? You can easily <strong>upgrade to the full <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"  href="/courses/rya-competent-crew">RYA Competent Crew</a></strong> course by extending your sailing to 5 days ‚Äî a perfect way to deepen your skills and confidence on the water.</p>
