                      <p>In the evening, enjoy a relaxed night in the harbour together ‚Äì cook on board or try a local Greek taverna ‚Äì wander the charming streets, and watch a stunning sunset. Then retreat to your cabin for a peaceful night, gently rocked by the boat, ready to start the next day full of new skills and adventures.</p>
